---
title: Moroccan-Inspired Chicken Thigh with Zucchini, Zesty Rice and Lemony Yogurt
description: This one's in the running to be your next weeknight fave. Warm, fragrant spices and creamy yogurt are a perfect, quick marinade for chicken thighs, while zesty rice rounds out the flavours of this delicious Moroccan-inspired plate.
